 sealable jar or container in the refrigerator for up to 1 month.","You can use dried chillies in this recipe. Simply soak in boiling water for 1 hour before using in step 6 (and omit fresh chillies).","This recipe makes 345 g total."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","25m","1 total recipe"]}